description.en:
The TEWKEN token captures the network value of the Tewkenaire Network and allows everyone in the TRON community to participate passively. TEWKEN is scarce, it has progressive mining difficulty and limited max supply of 100 million.

Tewkenaire is a community driven ecosystem of smart-contracts that distributes cryptocurrency rewards to its users.
There are eight smart-contracts on the Tewkenaire Network (Tewkenity, Hexmax, Hextew, Hexrise, Infinitew, Stable(TRX), Stable(ETH) and Crazy).
